      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Model setup procedures documented in a controlled simulation plan (SP-2023-004). Independent peer review of boundary conditions, load application, and material assignments performed by a second analyst not involved in model construction. No use errors identified during review."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
