      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level of 3.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 standard test condition (static, room temperature, displacement-controlled at 5 mm/min). No variation in loading rate, temperature, or cyclic pre-conditioning was explored. Achieved Gradation 2 — single standardized condition without parametric variation. This factor is below required level and represents a known limitation of the validation dataset."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
