      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA inputs match test specimen parameters; achieved level meets required.",
      "rationale": "FEA geometry parameterized directly from CMM measurements of each of the 11 bench specimens individually. Material properties assigned from lot-specific coupon data. Boundary conditions (UHMWPE block dimensions, loading fixture geometry) replicated from laboratory setup drawings. Equivalency confirmed by pre-test prediction protocol."
    },
    {
