      "acceptanceCriteria": "E/uval < 1.96 and absolute relative error < 10% for all primary QoIs.",
      "rationale": "Three QoIs compared: construct stiffness (E/uval=0.87, ARE=4.2%), yield force (E/uval=1.41, ARE=6.8%), force at 40 mm (E/uval=1.63, ARE=7.9%). All within pre-specified acceptance bounds. Validation uncertainty uval computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 5.3 incorporating experimental uncertainty and numerical uncertainty."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
