      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in ASTM F1717 and referenced in FDA guidance for spinal implant 510(k) submissions. These QoIs directly characterize structural performance relevant to the clinical failure mode (fatigue and overload fracture). High relevance confirmed by regulatory context."
