    "rationale": "The FEA modeling framework satisfies acceptance criteria for all three primary QoIs (E/uval < 1.96, ARE < 10%). Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors are assessed; eleven meet or exceed required levels. The Test conditions factor achieves Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3, which is noted but judged acceptable given the standardized ASTM F1717 protocol and inter-laboratory consistency. The overall credibility evidence is judged sufficient to support a Medium assurance level conclusion. The package is accepted for submission.",
